    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors and determined that the model is accepted for the intended COU. The majority of factors meet or exceed required levels, and the overall body of evidence supports a High assurance level determination. The team notes that the mesh convergence assessment was conducted with two meshes rather than three; however, the team judged this acceptable given the qualitative agreement observed and the overall validation performance. The High assurance level is declared based on the breadth of validation evidence and the satisfactory output comparison results.",
